<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٠٣٣ - ص ل ط ح]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صلطحَ يصلطح، صلطحةً، فهو مُصَلْطِح، والمفعول مُصَلْطَح<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• صلطح الشَّيءَ:</span> بَسَطَه وعرَّضه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>